<div class="standard-form">
    <p class="notes" style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: #ccc;">
        請選擇要導出的頻道分頁。導出過程會將所有圖片轉換為內嵌格式，這可能需要幾秒鐘的時間。
    </p>

    <div class="form-group-stacked" style="max-height: 300px; overflow-y: auto; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2); padding: 5px; border: 1px solid #444;">
        {{#each tabs}}
        <label class="checkbox" style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 4px;">
            <input type="checkbox" name="{{this.id}}" {{#if this.checked}}checked{{/if}}>
            <span style="margin-left: 5px;">{{this.label}}</span>
        </label>
        {{/each}}
    </div>

    <footer class="sheet-footer flexrow" style="margin-top: 10px; gap: 5px;">
        <button type="submit" data-action="doExport" style="background: #2d4f2d; color: #fff;">
            <i class="fas fa-file-export"></i> 開始導出
        </button>
    </footer>
</div>